---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="What I do · AroraMSP"
  description="Microsoft 365 service areas: Intune deployment, Entra ID and Conditional Access, Exchange Online migrations, Windows LAPS, PowerShell automation, hybrid Entra environments."
  page="whatido"
  canonical="https://aroramsp.com/whatido"
  ogTitle="What I Do - AroraMSP Microsoft 365 Consulting"
  ogDescription="Microsoft 365 security audits, Entra ID, Conditional Access, Exchange Online, Intune deployment, and PowerShell automation for organizations globally."
>
  <meta slot="head" name="keywords" content="Intune deployment, Entra ID Conditional Access, Exchange Online migration, Windows LAPS, PowerShell automation, hybrid Entra ID, Microsoft 365 consulting" />

  <section class="page wrap">
    <div class="page-head">
      <div class="sec-label">What I Do</div>
      <h1>Service areas.</h1>
      <p>Six focus areas where I do most of my engagements. Hands-on engineering rather than advisory: I write the scripts, run the migrations, and stay on the line through cutover.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="layout-2col">
      <div class="service-list">
        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <span class="tag">// endpoint management</span>
          <h3>Intune Deployment and Management</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Device compliance policies for Windows, iOS, Android, macOS</li>
            <li>App protection policies for managed and unmanaged devices</li>
            <li>Autopilot enrollment and zero-touch provisioning</li>
            <li>Windows Update for Business rings and patch management</li>
            <li>Defender for Endpoint integration and baseline policies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <span class="tag">// identity and access</span>
          <h3>Entra ID and Conditional Access</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Conditional Access policy design and implementation</li>
            <li>MFA enforcement and authentication strength policies</li>
            <li>Privileged Identity Management and role assignments</li>
            <li>External identities, guest access, and B2B collaboration</li>
            <li>Break-glass account configuration and monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <span class="tag">// email and collaboration</span>
          <h3>Exchange Online and Email Security</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>SPF, DKIM, DMARC configuration and verification</li>
            <li>Anti-phishing, anti-spam, and safe links policies</li>
            <li>Shared mailbox governance and licence optimization</li>
            <li>Mailbox migration from on-premises Exchange</li>
            <li>External forwarding controls and audit logging</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <span class="tag">// endpoint security</span>
          <h3>Windows LAPS</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>LAPS policy deployment via Intune</li>
            <li>Entra ID LAPS escrow configuration</li>
            <li>Hybrid Entra registration troubleshooting</li>
            <li>Account name compatibility across OS versions</li>
            <li>Post-deployment escrow verification via Graph</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <span class="tag">// automation</span>
          <h3>PowerShell and Graph API Automation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Microsoft Graph PowerShell automation scripts</li>
            <li>Tenant health audit and reporting scripts</li>
            <li>Mailbox storage and quota reporting</li>
            <li>Bulk user and licence management</li>
            <li>Scheduled automation via Azure Automation or Logic Apps</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <span class="tag">// hybrid infrastructure</span>
          <h3>Hybrid Entra Environments</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Entra Connect installation and configuration</li>
            <li>Hybrid Entra join troubleshooting and remediation</li>
            <li>Password hash sync and seamless SSO setup</li>
            <li>Staged rollout planning for cloud-only migration</li>
            <li>AD Connect health monitoring and alerting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="toolkit-aside reveal">
        <div class="sec-label">Get the Toolkit</div>
        <h3>AroraMSP M365 Audit Toolkit</h3>
        <div class="price"><span class="currency">USD</span>99</div>
        <ul class="includes-list">
          <li>M365 tenant security audit script (20 checks)</li>
          <li>Mailbox storage and quota report script</li>
          <li>Full app registration setup guide</li>
          <li>Sample HTML reports showing actual output</li>
          <li>PowerShell 5.1 and 7 compatible</li>
          <li>Certificate-based authentication, no password prompts</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://aroramsp.lemonsqueezy.com/checkout/buy/c366ed46-07c7-4057-88db-5886b94b8ea7" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Buy Now · USD 99
        </a>
        <div class="sample-links">
          <a href="/blog/samples/M365-Audit-Report-Sample" class="sample-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View sample audit report <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/samples/Mailbox-Report-Sample" class="sample-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View sample mailbox report <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="consult-box reveal">
          <div class="consult-label">// included with every purchase</div>
          <p>Every purchase includes a free 30-minute onboarding call. We set up the app registration together, run the scripts against your tenant, and confirm the output is correct.</p>
          <p>Book via Microsoft Bookings after purchase. Link provided in your download.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/resources/AroraMSP-M365-Audit-Sample.pdf" class="btn btn-ghost download-pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Download sample audit report (PDF) <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <p class="download-note">See exactly what a real audit delivers. 20 pages. No email required.</p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
